!! Biblical Friendship
!!! What is Biblical Friendship
What makes biblical friendship special and different? Secular friendships are often built upon similar interests. Biblical friendship is centered on Christ. 

''Common Bond in Christ and United Pursuits Define Biblical Friendships''

Rather than serving as an end to itself. Biblical friendship is a way to serve God.

